OL,3,CAround 1,000 women swimmers take the
OL,4,Cplunge in record-breaking dip
OL,6,FAround 1000 cold-water swimmers have
OL,7,Ftaken the plunge in an extraordinary,
OL,8,Frecord-breaking sea-dip in the English
OL,9,FChannel.
OL,11,FThe Big Swim features two dips - one
OL,12,Fin Brighton and the other in Poole,
OL,13,FDorset.
OL,15,FThe event is the brainchild of
OL,16,FBrighton adventurer Nicky Chisholm -
OL,17,Fknown as 'PinkNicky'.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
