OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773662582
OL,3,CAround 1,000 women swimmers take the
OL,4,Cplunge in record-breaking dip
OL,6,FFor 2026's record-breaking event,
OL,7,FNicky has partnered with outdoor
OL,8,Fexpert Rosie Tanner of Land and Wave
OL,9,Fto organise a sea-based tribute to
OL,10,Ffemale resilience and community.
OL,12,FRosie said: "Land & Wave has long been
OL,13,Fcampaigning to get more women working
OL,14,Fand playing in the outdoors, so we're
OL,15,Fdelighted to be welcoming a huge
OL,16,FDorset contingent to The Big Swim."
OL,18,FThis year's official charity partner
OL,19,Fis Surfers Against Sewage (SAS).
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
