PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773662582
OL,3,CAround 1,000 women swimmers take the
OL,4,Cplunge in record-breaking dip
OL,6,FThe event aims to highlight the urgent
OL,7,Fneed for clean water and radical
OL,8,Freform in the water industry.
OL,10,FJo Morley, Head of Campaigns and
OL,11,FAdvocacy at SAS, said: "This is an
OL,12,Fepic event and every penny raised will
OL,13,Fhelp us fuel the fight for clean
OL,14,Fwaters.
OL,16,F"This is a watershed year, and as a
OL,17,Fcommunity of water users we are
OL,18,Fshouting louder than ever, urging the
OL,19,FGovernment to end profit from
OL,20,Fpollution.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
