PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1773662582
OL,3,CAround 1,000 women swimmers take the
OL,4,Cplunge in record-breaking dip
OL,6,F"Whilst we're hoping that sewage
OL,7,Fdoesn't disrupt this incredible swim,
OL,8,Fwater quality can be checked via the
OL,9,FSafer Seas and Rivers Service, a free
OL,10,Fapp providing real-time pollution
OL,11,Falerts.
OL,13,FBoth dips featured a special
OL,14,Fappearance by two RNLI crews.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/4
